ore":1,"quote":{"pid":"08f79dccbc4d53a3c630eb4e27db59937cb48a46","tid":2035702,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"歐盟成日講人權<br />\n睇住中國搞左香港廿幾年做過d乜<br />\n照同中共合作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"不嬲把口就講自由做就獨裁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係都唔會整檔歐盟出嚟啦，搞到又央行又共同貨幣仲要歐盟法規可以凌駕各國法律仲要歐洲法院可以推翻成員國嘅法院判決。<br />\n呢啲就係自稱自由主義，全球主義嘅所謂菁英，講到尾都係唯利是圖嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c311fa7915f3c5500de1953862cf66c2ffae93a3","tid":2035702,"uid":301585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f7417a9f91b36b6b2c6d2dbc6014759b7f726da","tid":2035702,"uid":70771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:42:28.000Z","msg":"似係繼續買兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"算係咁，前幾年根本all in 中國，依幾年歐洲本土右派，民族主義慢慢抬緊頭，歐盟依d垃圾兩邊都唔敢討好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}